Indirect evidence for the CνB
Relativistic neutrinos contribute to the radiation energy density of the universe ρR, typically parameterized in terms of the effective number of neutrino species Nν :

  
    
      
        
          ρ
          
            
              R
            
          
        
        =
        
          
            
              π
              
                2
              
            
